IntroText: OooOOOoh!  A new pupil!  I am the art|teacher Giuliana, but you can call me Julia.
How's the painting going new pupil?|Will you do a masterwork like Raphael?
So you know about the great|master Sandro Botticelli work?

Do I look like the beautiful Venus?

Keep the pose!  Let's make art!
